<refentry id="bif.While" xreflabel="While">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>While</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>While</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>While</refname>
<refpurpose>
Iterates over expressions while a condition is true
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
While[boolean-expression, statement-list]
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>While</function>
defines a block of statements to be executed repeatedly.
See the section on control structures for complete information.
</para>
</refsect1>

